Subject: The Emperor's New Clothes
Description: Come learn how to create a costume out of thin air. You can take everyday clothes and items and make them into something cool!  Get tips on dyeing fabrics and taking care of wigs, and lots of ideas for ways to finish your costume. Bring your costume for help with last minute adjustments.  Speakers include:Cyndee Richardson - Track: Costuming  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
